snippet.title: Floaty Fighters: Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Website: https://floatyfighters.com/
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1130510/Floaty_Fighters/
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/7m8vJRV
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ShatteredJGames

Floaty Fighters is a free-movement fighting game with a focus on projectile attacks. Each character has a unique playstyle with four base moves, and they all combo together. Being able to maximize the potential of your fighter is the key to the game.
